ingredients: ["32 oz. can pork and beans", "2 tsp. chili powder", "1/2 tsp. salt", "3 Tbsp. vinegar", "1 Tbsp. mustard", "3 Tbsp. molasses", "1/4 tsp. garlic powder", "1/3 c. onion", "2 Tbsp. catsup"]
directions: ["Chop onion.", "Combine all ingredients and place in baking dish. Bake at 400\u00b0 for 20 minutes or until thoroughly heated."]

title: Avocado And Shrimp Fettucine
ingredients: ["1 Tbsp. butter", "1 tsp. minced garlic", "2 Tbsp. minced fresh parsley", "1/2 lb. shrimp, peeled and deveined", "2 Tbsp. dry vermouth or white wine", "3 Tbsp. butter", "1/2 c. heavy cream", "1/4 c. freshly grated Parmesan cheese", "dash of salt and ground pepper", "9 oz. fettucine, cooked and drained", "1 avocado, pitted, peeled and cubed"]
directions: ["In large skillet, heat 1 tablespoon butter over medium heat; add minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.", "Add parsley, shrimp and vermouth and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly, until shrimp turns pink.", "Do not overcook.", "Transfer to small bowl."]

title: Cottage Cheese Meat Loaf
ingredients: ["1 c. small curd cottage cheese", "1 egg, lightly beaten", "1/4 c. ketchup", "2 Tbsp. chopped onion", "1 Tbsp. prepared mustard", "1/2 c. quick cooking oats", "1 tsp. salt", "1/8 tsp. pepper", "1 lb. lean ground beef", "1/3 c. grated Parmesan cheese"]
directions: ["In a bowl, combine the first eight ingredients. Add beef and mix well. Press into an ungreased 8-inch square baking pan. Bake at 350\u00b0 for 20 minutes. Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese. Bake 10 to 15 minutes longer or until meat is no longer pink. Drain. Let stand 10 minutes before cutting. Yield: 4 servings."]

title: Peanut Butter Cookies
ingredients: ["1 c. crunchy peanut butter", "1 c. sugar", "1 egg, lightly beaten", "36 Hershey Kisses"]
directions: ["Roll in 3/4-inch balls.", "Place on ungreased cookie sheets. Bake 10 minutes at 350\u00b0.", "Immediately put Kisses in center of cookies. Remove cookies and place on wire rack to cool."]
